{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "819db441-d63b-4890-8329-980ba2a1fc1e", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/819db441-d63b-4890-8329-980ba2a1fc1e@1.pkg/1772597580851/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597581549", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/819db441-d63b-4890-8329-980ba2a1fc1e@1.pkg/1772597580851/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597581549"}, "identifier": "819db441-d63b-4890-8329-980ba2a1fc1e", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">A项：广东对西藏实行教育帮扶是为了促进当地教育的发展，不能实现民族融合，表述错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">B项：广东教育援藏工作属于教育帮扶，并非提供物质保障。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">C项：题干并未涉及区域协调发展，不符合题意。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">D项：</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">从题意可知，广东教育援藏工作通过&ldquo;组团式&rdquo;帮扶，加强教师队伍建设，补足当地教育发展短板，进而缩小教育差距，促进教育公平。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（原创）自1994年对口援藏工作开展以来，广东教育援藏工作坚持输血与造血并行，通过&ldquo;组团式&rdquo;帮扶，加强教师队伍建设，补足当地教育发展短板。广东教育援藏工作旨在（ &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（原创）自1994年对口援藏工作开展以来，广东教育援藏工作坚持输血与造血并行，通过“组团式”帮扶，加强教师队伍建设，补足当地教育发展短板。广东教育援藏工作旨在（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/819db441-d63b-4890-8329-980ba2a1fc1e@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754815188958", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">深化两地交往，实现民族融合</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">提供物质保障，促进共同繁荣</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">协调区域发展，建设教育强国</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">缩小教育差距，促进教育公平</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（原创）自1994年对口援藏工作开展以来，广东教育援藏工作坚持输血与造血并行，通过&ldquo;组团式&rdquo;帮扶，加强教师队伍建设，补足当地教育发展短板。广东教育援藏工作旨在（ &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "